text.tspan: The FDM and gaugea are simulated with JSBSim
The 3D model has more 3.5 million of vertices
Complete simulation of all on-board systems (fuel, hydraulic, oxigen, electtric)
Pilot assistant for a completely autonomous flight and terrain following
If you want to fly, we recommend that you read the original flight manual
The original declassified NATO flight manual is present
